    "This was mainly because of publications that developed novel processing methods and tested them on different tasks.",
    "We had ten main task groups alongside an extra group Other Tasks, which includes tasks with fewer than three publications each.",
    "Figure 5 shows an UpSet Plot to visualize the connections between all 11 learning tasks.",
    "Similar to the research domains, out of the 77 publications, 52 were categorized under only one learning task.",
    "Activity, or Stimuli Inference holds publications that focus on predicting the activity or stimulus based on the assumption that different stimuli and activities produce different scanpath data."
